                                        <li>You must provide accurate information and keep it updated.</li>
                                        <li>Some features require verification (e.g., selling, bidding, rentals).</li>
                                        <li>You are responsible for your account security and activity.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section id="platform" class="legal-anchor mb-4">
                                    <div class="section-title">
                                        <i class="bi bi-shield-exclamation text-warning"></i>
                                        <span>2) Platform usage rules</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-2">
                                        <span class="pill"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i>No fraud</span>
                                        <span class="pill"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i>No abuse</span>
                                        <span class="pill"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i>No spam</span>
                                        <span class="pill"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success"></i>Respect others</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Do not upload illegal, harmful, or misleading content.</li>
                                        <li>Do not attempt to bypass security, payment flow, or verification rules.</li>
                                        <li>We may suspend or block accounts violating rules.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section id="listings" class="legal-anchor mb-4">
                                    <div class="section-title">
                                        <i class="bi bi-shop text-success"></i>
                                        <span>3) Listings & content</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Listings must be accurate (price, availability, description, photos).</li>
                                        <li>Seller/Owner is responsible for fulfillment and quality.</li>
                                        <li>We can remove content that violates policy or is suspicious.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section id="orders" class="legal-anchor mb-4">
                                    <div class="section-title">
                                        <i class="bi bi-bag-check text-info"></i>
                                        <span>4) Orders, deposits & cancellations</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Some orders require a deposit before confirmation.</li>
                                        <li>Cancellation windows may apply (depending on store type).</li>
                                        <li>Auctions: deposit rules apply; refunds depend on outcome and policy.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section id="wallet" class="legal-anchor mb-4">
                                    <div class="section-title">
                                        <i class="bi bi-wallet2 text-warning"></i>
                                        <span>5) Wallet & payments</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>Wallet balance may include available and reserved amounts (holds).</li>
                                        <li>Payment providers may apply their own terms for card processing.</li>
                                        <li>Chargebacks and disputes may result in holds or restrictions.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section id="disputes" class="legal-anchor mb-4">
                                    <div class="section-title">
                                        <i class="bi bi-life-preserver text-success"></i>
                                        <span>6) Disputes & enforcement</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>We may request evidence from both parties (messages, receipts, images).</li>
                                        <li>We may freeze disputed amounts until resolution.</li>
                                        <li>Repeated abuse may lead to suspension or permanent ban.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section id="liability" class="legal-anchor mb-4">
                                    <div class="section-title">
                                        <i class="bi bi-exclamation-octagon text-danger"></i>
                                        <span>7) Liability</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <ul class="mb-0">
                                        <li>The platform provides marketplace functionality "as is".</li>
                                        <li>We are not responsible for third-party listings accuracy.</li>
                                        <li>We are not liable for indirect losses (unless required by law).</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </section>

                                <section id="changes" class="legal-anchor">
                                    <div class="section-title">
                                        <i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat text-secondary"></i>
                                        <span>8) Changes to these terms</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="mb-0">
                                        We may update these terms to reflect new features or legal requirements.
                                        Continued use means you accept the updated terms.
                                    </p>

                                    <div class="mt-3 d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <a class="btn btn-success auth-btn-success" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">
                                            <i class="bi bi-shield-lock me-1"></i>Privacy Policy
                                        </a>
                                        <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary rounded-pill px-3" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                                            <i class="bi bi-house me-1"></i>Back to Home
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </section>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>